svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 01, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tmn1665703045400.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tmn1665703045400.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tmn1665703045400.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tmn1665703045400\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Database I/O Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tmn1665703045400__ul_blr_gjb_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jlp1665702702609.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jlp1665702702609.html\" title=\"Defines how an entity will access the data store—via a database path, or via an entity service.\">Data Access</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcg1665702702535.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcg1665702702535.html\" title=\"Determines whether the entity is stored in a database. If N, the Data Access and Database Path property values are ignored.\">Database Behavior</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aww1665702586248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aww1665702586248.html\" title=\"Uniface data type to use for this field, variable, or parameter. The default value is S (String).\">Data Type</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yyf1665702556802.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yyf1665702556802.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the field interface) determines how data in the field is physically stored in the database.\">Database Interface (Fields)</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cyp1665702702678.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyp1665702702678.html\" title=\"DBMS path to use when storing occurrences of this entity. This is a named route to the Uniface DBMS connector used to connect to the database. Valid values are Uniface default paths ($DEF, $SYS, $UUU), supported databases and file formats, and user-defined paths. The default is DEF.\">Database Path</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rlk1665702702767.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rlk1665702702767.html\" title=\"Specifies the signature of the Entity Service component that will handle data access. Applicable only if Database Access is Y (Via Entity Service).\">Entity Service</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jmg1665702703110.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jmg1665702703110.html\" title=\"Specifies the component entity fields that Uniface manages at runtime. Valid values are Automatic (default), All Fields, and User-defined.\">Field List</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpv1665702557117.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpv1665702557117.html\" title=\"Property that specifies how the field's data is formatted for display. The value can be a comma-separated list of shorthand codes, or a reference to a modeled field layout.\">Field Layout</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wen1665702586573.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wen1665702586573.html\" title=\"Value that should be displayed in this field at runtime; can be a default for the user or the actual field value.\">Initial Value</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iku1665702689266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iku1665702689266.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to interpret field data upon input.\">Input Translation</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oji1665702586488.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oji1665702586488.html\" title=\"Determines whether the field is a control field in a form component, meaning that it can be selected with the mouse but not get focus. This affects validation behavior.\">Is Control</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pta1665702586322.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pta1665702586322.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.\">Is External</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iri1665702586413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iri1665702586413.html\" title=\"Determines whether the field contents are same for all occurrences of the entity.\">Is Static</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nle1665702702840.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nle1665702702840.html\" title=\"Locking strategy to use when saving data for this entity. Valid values are Cautious (default), Optimistic, or No Updates.\">Locking</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"djr1665702702912.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/djr1665702702912.html\" title=\"Minimum number of occurrences this entity must have in the component data structure. This number is checked by Uniface before occurrences can be removed.\">Minimum Occurrences</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xzc1665702703040.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzc1665702703040.html\" title=\"Maximum number of records this entity can have in the component data structure. This number is checked by Uniface before occurrences can be added.\">Maximum Occurrences</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbe1665702689335.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbe1665702689335.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to convert field data upon output.\">Output Translation</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616131\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616131\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database I/O Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 01, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Database I/O Properties Data Access Database Behavior Data Type Database Interface (Entities) Database Interface (Fields) Database Path Entity Service Field List Field Layout Field Syntax Initial Value Input Translation Is Control Is External Is Static Locking Minimum Occurrences Maximum Occurrences Output Translation Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}